{"tid":532179,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【平昌冬奧】南北韓敲定　奧運開幕式共舉半島旗入場","createTime":"2018-01-17T14:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T00:10:24.000Z","uid":84436,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"34c1accea0110e485b40bdb08f0d20390ddaa5e6","tid":532179,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:30:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180117/1280713/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180117%2F1280713%2F&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8B4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=25c34cdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180117%2F1280713%2F&h=4f48f71b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180117/1280713/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩韓代表今天繼續商談北韓參加冬季奧運事宜，南韓政府剛剛表示，雙方已經同意在冬季奧運開幕式持「朝鮮半島旗」（又稱統一旗）一同入場。<br />\n<br />\n本屆冬季奧運在南韓平昌舉行，兩韓代表商議後，決定兩韓共組女子冰球隊，而北韓提議代表團由「西海線陸路」進入南韓，「西海線陸路」是指經由開城工業區的路線。<br />\n <br />\n除了北韓奧委會代表、體育選手、30人的跆拳道示範團、記者團之外，北韓將派出230人啦啦隊，這些色藝雙全的啦啦隊員多來自北韓專門的藝術教育學校「金星學院」，每次到南韓表演總成熱門話題，北韓第一夫人李雪主同樣出自金星學院，也曾以啦啦隊員身分赴南韓。<br />\n<br />\n另外，北韓也同意派出150人的代表團參加冬季帕奧，帕奧將於3月9日至18日在平昌舉行。兩韓尚未決定北韓代表團在南韓期間的旅費要怎樣支付，如果南韓代為支付，直接給予現金資助，將會違反聯合國安理會的制裁禁令，所以可能必須透過兩韓經濟協力基金會居中處理。此外，除了運動選手之外，北韓已決定派出140人的管弦樂團、230人的啦啦隊，如果南韓要負擔全體代表的旅費，將是一筆不小的費用。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"ccb0f015aa5013211c976aad27c3b3f57fa4818e","tid":532179,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"圖都冇張"},{"pid":"3a1d5997481a8f62e8b589b66e9660d8a8e9d329","tid":532179,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27aa6a06b9333cfcae9a4410cf34b1e2c3e5f27","tid":532179,"uid":69269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T15:52:15.000Z","msg":"啱啦南北韓應該一早一體化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb88a3bfc7e8126714aaab69fd09249415ab0a93","tid":532179,"uid":59835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n如果奧運後有北韓選手留係南泡<br />\n會否開戰"},{"pid":"78dd6092fb15d399735b1f60d31b8af5d3b31f8f","tid":532179,"uid":41138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:15:17.000Z","msg":"北韓做國家體育代表使唔使殺過下人先？（台拳道）"},{"pid":"66499c3fefb1d4c934219e10cc3a3d5008f793ef","tid":532179,"uid":5963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T22:24:33.000Z","msg":"北韓會唔會其實扮撚晒野，放人開南韓波，第三次世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61ef19dc547bf5e69346d8327af1a36a59ccc09","tid":532179,"uid":24168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T23:34:59.000Z","msg":"木馬屠城"},{"pid":"d2f73d2d19e5eada6e525e4d8c9bacceb186b815","tid":532179,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T23:59:46.000Z","msg":"統一旗或朝鮮半島旗（韓半島旗），為北韓與南韓的運動員在大型運動會上共同走入會場所使用的代表整個朝鮮半島的旗幟。早在1991年在日本千葉市舉行的第41屆世界乒乓球錦標賽和葡萄牙里斯本舉行的第6屆世界青年足球錦標賽上，朝韓雙方使用該旗入場。隨後在2000年、2004年和2006年的奧運會、澳門東亞運以及2006年多哈亞運會上，朝韓雙方也使用此旗幟共同入場。但是雖然雙方在諸多場合共同入場，但比賽時仍然各自為一隊。朝韓雙方在澳門東亞運的團長會議以外時間開始就2008年組成「聯合隊伍」的統一問題進行了磋商，但北京奧委會在奧運開幕式前證實，朝韓兩隊在北京奧運開幕式上將分開入場。"},{"pid":"87892861ae1e7bf9b998d1390f25b201d8a752bc","tid":532179,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photo.sohu.com/42/24/Img165042442.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphoto.sohu.com%2F42%2F24%2FImg165042442.jpg&h=5f0c1668&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c84c7af638f43f24290bdf02f233edcb6bb1ab1","tid":532179,"uid":132038,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:02:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b79fb74b721e2c08d5211ff42fa9bb372d81293","tid":532179,"uid":619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:08:36.000Z","msg":"開幕禮就開幕禮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8e0eeebec6b4e14c75d1dd19b7bd75d523b254","tid":532179,"uid":87573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:10:24.000Z","msg":"金仔先係真正政治家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}